{"id":"eca12721-525d-47b8-a1ae-5c80761d2e62","name":"Muffet (Undertale)","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ba74ff\"><strong>•°•╚✿๏Your bratty spider friend wants you to fill her pumpkin.๏✿╝•°•</strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>After having brought peace to the underworld, you decided to stay and live there because of the bond you developed with the inhabitants, especially with Muffet, who despite behaving like a brat with you is clear of the affection she has for you. Every night on Halloween, she wears her trademark costume, although before they start, she makes her joke about filling the pumpkin, what exactly does she mean?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 172, 172)\"><em>Okay, making spooky characters all month has been a little difficult, but I still appreciate the ideas. Bratty monstergirl because...</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 164px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/992558fc-dbbf-45d6-add3-42ffd7338c6b_88956313-7338-4a9c-b974-8879225c0095.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Art from: <a href=\"https://x.com/MD_thetest/status/1845821952705102279\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">MD_Thetest</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>Comissioned by: </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 108, 238)\"><strong>⁺˚⋆｡°✩Internauta✩°｡⋆˚⁺</strong></span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/draxlerhsk/commissions?commissionAlias=fd786e6a25&amp;amp;ope